WHY JOIN THE TEAM?

The Global Retail & Sales, a division within Powersports Group, is looking for an experienced Senior Manager Data Science & Analytics to join our team in order to bring the analytics practice to the next level. We are looking for a self-motivated individual who thrives in a dynamic fast-paced environment. You are an analysis expert who

leverages a variety of platforms and analytical tools to extract critical insights from massive data sets. You have hands-on experience working in an analytical environment, with a deep understanding of data mining and analytical techniques. In this role you will implement world-class analytical solutions and help make analytics a bold advantage for BRP.

In addition to advanced analytic skills, you are skilled at integrating and preparing large, varied datasets, designing and implementing production algorithm, and communicating results. You are primarily a data scientist but are passionate about developing advanced end-to-end analytics that create value for our business.

YOUR KEY RESPONSIBILITIES
Lead the development of the analytics practice and provide business expertise;
Develop analytics solutions to support insight generation while integrating modern AI technics to increase analytics depth;
Lead large complex analytics projects to optimize our market positioning and enhance our dealer value proposition;
Extract, cleanse, and combine data from multiple sources and systems;
Perform exploratory analysis, with a wide variety of statistical methods including: cluster, regression, decision tree, random forest, time series, neural network and others;
