Langan has an opportunity for an Environmental Scientist or Biologist - 5 to 10 Years Experience in our Calgary, AB office location. The successful candidate will be responsible for performing duties as a field representative, including: pre-reclamation assessments; Detailed Site Assessments (DSA); invasive weed surveys; wetland delineations; rare plant surveys; wildlife surveys; reclamation oversight; restoration monitoring, collecting field data and samples; monitoring construction sites, compiling data, and preparing reports.

Job Responsibilities:
Conduct plant and wildlife surveys for habitat assessments, special-status species, and other project requirements;
Conduct wetland delineations, jurisdictional determinations, and other aquatic resource surveys using current agency protocols, regionally specific methods, and other guidance;
